            <title><![CDATA[Marathon: Everything You Need To Know About Launch Times, Pre-Load, Server Slam Rewards, And More]]></title>
            <link>https://gameinformer.com/psa/2026/03/04/marathon-release-timing-confirmed-alongside-other-launch-day-faqs</link>
