  </picture>


  
  
  
</article>

<p>The final release build of Marathon will include the full suite of the game's progression systems, a new Runner shell, Outpost, and the following:&nbsp;</p><ul><li>Full faction and contract progression</li><li>All six factions, including Sekiguchi Genetics</li><li>All six launch Runner shells, including Thief</li><li>Three zones, including Outpost<ul><li>Outpost will unlock the day after launch (so March 6) to give players time to gear up and unlock the zone at Runner Level 12</li></ul></li><li>28 weapons, plus mods, implants, cores, and more to craft your Runner builds</li><li>Earnable cosmetics, achievements, and storytelling through the Codex</li></ul><p>Bungie says the final release of Marathon includes fixes and updates informed by the recent Server Slam, including adjustments to PvP frequency on Perimeter (Beginner), with more changes to come.&nbsp;</p><h3>Cryo Archive</h3><p>Cryo Archive</p>



