<p>Players on PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, and Steam will receive weapon charms unique to their platform.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><p>PlayStation players will receive the For Freedom, Battle Guitar, and Onryō weapon charms, and must visit the PlayStation Store to claim them when Marathon launches.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>Xbox players will automatically receive the Emerald Clutch and Emerald Catch weapon charms upon logging in at launch.&nbsp;</p></li><li><p>Steam players will automatically receive the Crowbar weapon charm upon logging in at launch.&nbsp;</p></li></ul><h3>Marathon Login Queues</h3><p>Marathon Login Queues&nbsp;</p>



