<p>Bungie expects login queues on Marathon's launch day and says it will communicate status updates if it needs to perform maintenance via the&nbsp;Bungie Server Status accounts <a href="https://x.com/BNGServerStatus">on X</a> and&nbsp;<a href="https://bsky.app/profile/bungiehelp.bungie.net">Bluesky</a>. It will also share updates in the <a href="https://discord.com/invite/marathonthegame">Marathon community Discord</a>.&nbsp;</p><h3>Reporting Marathon Issues</h3><p>Reporting Marathon Issues</p>



