<ul><li>Visit Bungie's <a href="https://help.bungie.net/hc/en-us">Help pages and forums</a> on Bungie.net for troubleshooting and known issues. If you run into reward delivery problems, account linking errors, or crashes, this is a good place to start.</li><li>You can also join the <a href="https://discord.com/invite/marathonthegame">official Marathon Discord</a> and follow <a href="https://x.com/MarathonDevTeam">MarathonDevTeam on X</a> for alerts or to ask for help.&nbsp;</li></ul><p>And that's everything you need to know for Marathon's launch on March 5! If we're missing anything, let us know in the comments below!</p></div></div><br/><br/>https://gameinformer.com/psa/2026/03/04/marathon-release-timing-confirmed-alongside-other-launch-day-faqs]]></content:encoded>
